### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Create project
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo Project",
  "description": "Проект для проверки lexical и semantic retrieval в user_service"
}

### List projects
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/projects

### Get project by id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/projects/1

### Create regression run - lexical
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/projects/1/regression-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "change_summary": "Изменен экран логина, добавлена валидация email и обработка ошибки 401",
  "candidate_limit": 5,
  "search_mode": "lexical"
}

### Create regression run - semantic
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/projects/1/regression-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "change_summary": "Изменен экран логина, добавлена валидация email и обработка ошибки 401",
  "candidate_limit": 5,
  "search_mode": "semantic"
}

### List regression runs
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/projects/1/regression-runs

### Get regression run by id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/regression-runs/1